          <div class="accordion-inner">
            <p>
              <strong><a href="http://smokefree.gov/apps" target="_blank">Smokefree Apps</a></strong> help you track cravings, monitor progress, and give you strategies to help you become smokefree.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div></div>    <div class="accordion-group">
       <div class="accordion-heading accordion-toggle extra_help collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion1">
              <a class="accordion-toggle toggle-arrow collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion1" href="https://smokefree.gov/build-your-quit-plan">
                <span class="sr-only">Toggle Craving</span>
              </a>
