                <span class="sr-only">Toggle Craving</span>
              </a>
              <div class="fancy-checkbox-wrap"><div class="form-item form-item-extra-help-helplivehelp form-type-checkbox checkbox"><span class="element-invisible">NCI LiveHelp </span><input class="fancy bind-change form-checkbox" id="help.livehelp" data-ga-action="Help" data-ga-label="livehelp" type="checkbox" name="extra_help[help.livehelp]" value="help.livehelp"></div><label for="help.livehelp"><span><span></span></span>NCI LiveHelp</label></div></div>        <div id="help-collapse-6" class="accordion-body collapse">
          <div class="accordion-inner">
            <p>Get help quitting through an online chat with a smoking cessation counselor. LiveHelp is offered Monday through Friday, 8:00 a.m. to 11:00 p.m. Eastern Time. <a href="https://livehelp.cancer.gov/app/chat/chat_launch/" target="_blank">Visit the NCI LiveHelp page to chat with a counselor.</a></p>
