              <div class="fancy-checkbox-wrap"><div class="form-item form-item-extra-help-helpmedicationsf form-type-checkbox checkbox"><span class="element-invisible">Medication and Nicotine Replacement Therapy (NRT) </span><input class="fancy bind-change form-checkbox" id="help.medicationSF" data-ga-action="Help" data-ga-label="medicationSF" type="checkbox" name="extra_help[help.medicationSF]" value="help.medicationSF"></div><label for="help.medicationSF"><span><span></span></span>Medication and Nicotine Replacement Therapy (NRT)</label></div></div>         <div id="help-collapse-6" class="accordion-body collapse">
            <div class="accordion-inner">
              <p>Using <a href="http://smokefree.gov/explore-medications" target="_blank">medications and/or nicotine replacement therapy (NRT)</a> can improve your chances of quitting for good. Make an appointment with your health care provider to find out which options are best for you.</p>
